title: Will Trump's Missile Strikes in Syria make a Difference? - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 4/7/17
itunes:title: Will Trump's Missile Strikes in Syria make a Difference? - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 4/7/17
description:
George Noory and an open lines caller debate whether the US missile strikes in response to the alleged chemical weapons attacks in Syria will deter further violence in the region.
